#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.1&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;40px|40px|40px|40px|true|true&#8221; custom_padding_tablet=&#8221;40px|40px|40px|40px|true|true&#8221; custom_padding_phone=&#8221;40px|20px|40px|20px|true|true&#8221; custom_padding_last_edited=&#8221;on|tablet&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; header_2_line_height=&#8221;1.2em&#8221; header_3_font=&#8221;Poppins|500||on|||||&#8221; header_3_font_size=&#8221;14px&#8221; header_3_letter_spacing=&#8221;4px&#8221; header_3_line_height=&#8221;1.4em&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||0px|||&#8221; custom_padding_tablet=&#8221;|10%|||false|false&#8221; custom_padding_phone=&#8221;|10%|||false|false&#8221; custom_padding_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; text_font_size_tablet=&#8221;14px&#8221; text_font_size_phone=&#8221;13px&#8221; text_font_size_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; header_2_font_size_tablet=&#8221;&#8221; header_2_font_size_phone=&#8221;18px&#8221; header_2_font_size_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; locked=&#8221;off&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2>M\u00e5ttbest\u00e4llda persienner med montering<\/h2>\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Persienner, det klassiska solskyddet, \u00e4r enkla att hantera och kan snabbt regleras hur mycket sol, ljus eller insyn man \u00f6nskar f\u00f6r tillf\u00e4llet. Genom den m\u00e5ngfald som finns p\u00e5 olika persienners utseende g\u00e4llande f\u00e4rger och m\u00f6nster p\u00e5 lamellerna kan ni skapa er egen unika persienn.<\/p>\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">B\u00e4st i test-persiennen<\/h3>\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">V\u00e5r\u00a0\u201cb\u00e4st i test\u201d-persienn, Bellevue Persiennen, med sidoskenor \u00e4r ett persiennsystem\u00a0som \u00e4r patenterat och m\u00f6nsterskyddat. V\u00e5r<span data-color=\"transparent\">\u00a0<\/span><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/unika-funktioner\">unika l\u00f6sning<\/a><span data-color=\"transparent\">\u00a0<\/span>inneb\u00e4r att service- och monteringskostnader s\u00e4nks j\u00e4mf\u00f6rt med andra modeller p\u00e5 marknaden. Systemet har blivit prisat f\u00f6r sitt nyt\u00e4nkande och h\u00f6ga kvalit\u00e9t.<\/p>\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><\/h3>\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">M\u00e5ttanpassade persienner<\/h3>\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Persienner \u00e4r b\u00e5de funktionella och eleganta. Hos Bellevue Solskydd hittar du ett stort utbud som kombinerar stil med effektiv ljusreglering. Naturligtvis har vi \u00e4ven konventionella persiennvarianter som mellanglaspersienner och frih\u00e4ngande persienner. V\u00e5ra popul\u00e4ra persienner tillverkas med m\u00e5ttanpassning i Bellevue Solskydds lokaler i Malm\u00f6 f\u00f6r att passa alla olika typer av f\u00f6nster perfekt. Hos oss hittar ni persienner som kan regleras b\u00e5de manuellt och med motor, f\u00f6r en smidig och flexibel anv\u00e4ndarupplevelse.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/testfakta_bellevue-150&#215;150-1.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;testfakta_bellevue-150&#215;150 (1)&#8221; url=&#8221;\/persienner\/#persienn-hembasok&#8221; show_bottom_space=&#8221;off&#8221; align=&#8221;right&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; transform_translate=&#8221;30px|0px&#8221; transform_translate_linked=&#8221;off&#8221; transform_rotate=&#8221;0deg|0deg|10deg&#8221; position_origin_a=&#8221;center_center&#8221; position_origin_r=&#8221;bottom_right&#8221; width=&#8221;150px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||||false|false&#8221; animation_style=&#8221;slide&#8221; animation_direction=&#8221;right&#8