n type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_orientation=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2>Checklista f\u00f6r att v\u00e4lja r\u00e4tt persienner<\/h2>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_3,1_3,1_3&#8243; disabled_on=&#8221;on|on|off&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_3&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_icon font_icon=&#8221;&#xf545;||fa||900&#8243; icon_color=&#8221;#2c5268&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_icon][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_3&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_icon font_icon=&#8221;&#xf550;||fa||900&#8243; icon_color=&#8221;#2c5268&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_icon][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_3&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_icon font_icon=&#8221;&#xf095;||fa||900&#8243; icon_color=&#8221;#2c5268&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_icon][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_3,1_3,1_3&#8243; disabled_on=&#8221;on|on|off&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_3&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_orientation=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>M\u00e4t dina f\u00f6nster f\u00f6r att s\u00e4kerst\u00e4lla perfekt passform.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_3&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_orientation=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>V\u00e4lj mellan olika typer av persienner som mellanglas, frih\u00e4ngande eller sidoskenor.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_3&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_orientation=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Kontakta oss f\u00f6r r\u00e5dgivning och montering!<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Vanliga fr\u00e5gor om persienner<\/h3>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_accordion icon_color=&#8221;#000000&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Kan jag f\u00e5 persienner som \u00e4r m\u00e5ttanpassade?&#8221; open=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Ja vi p\u00e5 Bellevue Solskydd specialiserar p\u00e5 m\u00e5ttanpassade solskydd f\u00f6r b\u00e5de inomhus- och utomhusbruk. Vi levererar och monterar kompletta l\u00f6sningar f\u00f6r hem, kontor och offentliga milj\u00f6er.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Erbjuder ni gratis hembes\u00f6k? &#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Ja vi erbjuder ett kostnadsfritt hembes\u00f6k av en solskyddsexpert som ger tips och r\u00e5d kring persienner och hur de b\u00e4st passar ditt hem och dina \u00f6nskem\u00e5l. Detta erbjudande g\u00e4ller under f\u00f6ruts\u00e4ttning att Bellevue Solskydd \u00e4r med genom hela processen fr\u00e5n m\u00e5ttagning till montering.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Ing\u00e5r montering av persiennerna?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Ja Bellevue Solskydd levererar och monterar de m\u00e5ttbest\u00e4llda persiennerna enligt dina \u00f6nskem\u00e5l vilket s\u00e4kerst\u00e4ller en korrekt installation och funktion.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Vilka typer av persienner erbjuder ni? &#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Bellevue Solskydd erbjuder ett brett utbud av persienner inklusive klassiska mellanglaspersienner, frih\u00e4ngande persienner och deras prisbel\u00f6nta &#8221;<a href=\"https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/persienner\/\">B\u00e4st i Test<\/a>&#8221;-persienn med sidoskenor. Alla persienner \u00e4r m\u00e5ttanpassade och tillverkas i v\u00e5r lokal i Malm\u00f6 f\u00f6r att passa olika typer av f\u00f6nster perfekt.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Hur reng\u00f6r jag mina persienner?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Dammsug f\u00f6rsiktigt med borstmunstycke eller anv\u00e4nd en mjuk persiennborste. Det g\u00e5r ocks\u00e5 bra att spola av dem med vatten, t\u00e4nk d\u00e5 p\u00e5 persiennen skall torkas uth\u00e4ngd.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][\/et_pb_accordion][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; admin_label=&#8221;Featured Places&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; locked=&#8221;off&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2>Olika typer av persienner f\u00f6r alla behov<\/h2>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_4,1_4,1_4,1_4&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; animation_style=&#8221;fade&#8221; use_custom_width=&#8221;on&#8221; custom_width_px=&#8221;1440px&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; background_color=&#8221;#ffffff&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;||32px||false|false&#8221; border_radii=&#8221;on|5px|5px|5px|5px&#8221; border_width_all=&#8221;1px&#8221; border_color_all=&#8221;#E5DFD8&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/bellevue-med-sidoskenor.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;bellevue-med-sidoskenor&#8221; force_fullwidth=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; min_height_tablet=&#8221;&#8221; min_height_phone=&#8221;&#8221; min_height_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; height=&#8221;300px&#8221; height_tablet=&#8221;300px&#8221; height_phone=&#8221;300px&#8221; height_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][et_pb_toggle title=&#8221;Bellevue Standard (VST)&#8221; open_toggle_background_color=&#8221;RGBA(255,255,255,0)&#8221; closed_toggle_background_color=&#8221;RGBA(255,255,255,0)&#8221; icon_color=&#8221;gcid-c2933ceb-9641-4d37-bb1b-61eb067d45cb&#8221; open_icon_color=&#8221;gcid-c2933ceb-9641-4d37-bb1b-61eb067d45cb&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; title_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;-10px||||false|false&#8221; border_width_all=&#8221;0px&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{%22gcid-c2933ceb-9641-4d37-bb1b-61eb067d45cb%22:%91%22icon_color%22,%22open_icon_color%22%93}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Bellevue standard med sidoskenor \u00e4r v\u00e5r \u201dtopps\u00e4ljare\u201d och blev 2010 utn\u00e4mnd till \u201dB\u00e4st i Test\u201d av <a href=\"https:\/\/testfakta.se\/\" title=\"Testfakta\">Testfakta<\/a>. Med betyg 4,6 av 5 m\u00f6jliga och med kommentarer som \u201dB\u00e4st i Test och mest prisv\u00e4rd. Bra kvalitet, bra funktioner och mycket enkel att montera och demontera\u201d. Persiennkassetten \u00e4r v\u00e4ndbar som standard. Vid mindre fasade kanter finns 2 olika distanslister som tillval. Dekorlist ing\u00e5r. Linl\u00e5s och plexistav finns som tillval.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/BS_Monteringsanvisning_VST_A5-1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ladda ner Monteringsanvisning<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div class=\"et_pb_blurb_description\">\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/wp-content\/upload