rk&#8221; text_font_size_tablet=&#8221;15px&#8221; text_font_size_phone=&#8221;14px&#8221; text_font_size_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; header_font_size_tablet=&#8221;46px&#8221; header_font_size_phone=&#8221;32px&#8221; header_font_size_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; locked=&#8221;off&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2>Mer om v\u00e5ra persienner<\/h2>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_2,1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.1&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.2&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_line_height=&#8221;2em&#8221; header_3_font_size=&#8221;20px&#8221; header_3_line_height=&#8221;1.8em&#8221; header_3_font_size_tablet=&#8221;18px&#8221; header_3_font_size_phone=&#8221;16px&#8221; header_3_font_size_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; locked=&#8221;off&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Vad kostar persienner?<\/h3>\n<p>V\u00e5rt pris p\u00e5 persienner varierar beroende p\u00e5 en rad olika faktorer, bland annat dimensioner, materialval och hur omfattande arbetet \u00e4r. Vi str\u00e4var alltid efter att erbjuda h\u00f6gkvalitativa l\u00f6sningar till konkurrenskraftiga priser, som uppfyller dina behov och budget.<\/p>\n<p>F\u00f6r en mer exakt prisuppgift, rekommenderar vi att du <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/kontakt\/\">kontaktar oss<\/a> direkt f\u00f6r konsultation och en offert anpassad efter dina f\u00f6ruts\u00e4ttningar och \u00f6nskem\u00e5l.<\/p>\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Persienner tillverkade i Malm\u00f6<\/h3>\n<p>Alla persiennmodeller tillverkas i v\u00e5r fabrik i Malm\u00f6. Alla best\u00e5ndsdelarna i v\u00e5ra persienner \u00e4r svensktillverkade och \u00e4r noga utvalda f\u00f6r att vi skall kunna leverera produkter av absolut h\u00f6gsta kvalitet.<\/p>\n<h3>Montering:<\/h3>\n<p>Monteringsanvisningar finns till respektive modell.<\/p>\n<h3>Man\u00f6vrering:<\/h3>\n<p>Persiennerna regleras via lina samt en vridst\u00e5ng f\u00f6r att best\u00e4mma niv\u00e5 och vinkel\u00a0p\u00e5 lamellerna.<\/p>\n<h3>Dimensioner:<\/h3>\n<p>Min bredd: 23cm Max bredd: 300cm<\/p>\n<p>Min h\u00f6jd: Max h\u00f6jd: 300cm<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.1&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.1&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_line_height=&#8221;2em&#8221; header_3_font_size=&#8221;20px&#8221; header_3_line_height=&#8221;1.8em&#8221; header_3_font_size_tablet=&#8221;18px&#8221; header_3_font_size_phone=&#8221;16px&#8221; header_3_font_size_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; locked=&#8221;off&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3>M\u00e4tning:<\/h3>\n<p>M\u00e4t, helst p\u00e5 flera st\u00e4llen, det synliga glasdagerm\u00e5ttet (synlig glasruta) i mm fr\u00e5n tr\u00e4kant till tr\u00e4kant, insida. Bredd x h\u00f6jd i mm.<\/p>\n<p>OBS! Stumt m\u00e5tt, inga avdrag!<\/p>\n<p>Vid nytillverkade tr\u00e4f\u00f6nster s\u00e5 kan du l\u00e4mna f\u00f6nsterfabrikat, modellbeteckning och modulm\u00e5tt. Vi har glasdagerm\u00e5tten fr\u00e5n de st\u00f6rsta f\u00f6nstertillverkarna i Sverige.<\/p>\n<h3>F\u00e4rger:<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Lamell<span>\u00a0<\/span><span>*<\/span><span>\u00a0<\/span>\u2013 B4 Brun, B7 Beige, B10 Vit\/svart insida, B13 Ljusgr\u00e5, B20 Glittrig Aluminium, B22 Svart, B23 Gr\u00e5 Aluminium, B24 Antracit Gr\u00e5, B25 Mellangr\u00e5, B26 M\u00f6rkgr\u00e5, B27 Silver Perforerad.<\/li>\n<li>Stegband \u2013 Vit, brun<\/li>\n<li>Draglina \u2013 Vit, brun<\/li>\n<li>Styrlina \u2013 Vit, brun<\/li>\n<li>\u00d6verlist, underlist \u2013 Vit, brun<\/li>\n<li>Vridst\u00e5ng, st\u00e5ng\/linh\u00e5llare, kombibeslag, samt lintofs \u2013 Vit, brun<\/li>\n<li>Designlist \u2013 Vit, brun<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span>*\u00a0<em>Standardf\u00e4rger \u2013 andra f\u00e4rgval mot pristill\u00e4gg.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h3>Milj\u00f6information:<\/h3>\n<p>V\u00e5ra aluminiumlameller \u00e4r fria fr\u00e5n skadliga \u00e4mnen! F\u00e4rgen \u00e4r fri ifr\u00e5n bly, krom, arsenik etc.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.1&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color=&#8221;#F4F3EF&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||||false|false&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;0px||||false|false&#8221; locked=&#8221;off&#8221; collapsed=&#8221;on&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; admin_label=&#8221;Listings&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_module=&#8221;48603&#8243; saved_tabs=&#8221;all&#8221; locked=&#8221;off&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.2&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.1&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; text_line_height=&#8221;2em&#8221; header_3_font=&#8221;Poppins|500||on|||||&#8221; header_3_font_size=&#8221;14px&#8221; header_3_letter_spacing=&#8221;4px&#8221; header_3_line_height=&#8221;1.4em&#8221; text_font_size_tablet=&#8221;14px&#8221; text_font_size_phone=&#8221;&#8221; text_font_size_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; locked=&#8221;off&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3>Uppt\u00e4ck liknande produkter f\u00